<bioghist encodinganalog="545">
<p>Grace Bible Church in Ann Arbor, Michigan is an independent non-denominational church. The church began as a Bible study meeting in a home. The founding date of the church was 1935.</p>
</bioghist>


<scopecontent encodinganalog="520">
<p>The records include administrative files, topical files, women's groups, publication, and other materials. The administrative records series includes annual reports, minutes of the executive committee, and of congregational meetings.</p>
</scopecontent>

